{"TopicId":219928,"ForumId":201,"TopicTitle":"Flight View is Changing when Returning from Map View (Regularly Ending up in the Middle of a Craft)","CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-17T03:03:44Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Anth","CreatedById":161238,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-10-17T03:03:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EReported Version:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0v0.1.4.1 (latest) |\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003EMods:\u00A0\u003C/strong\u003Enone | \u003Cstrong\u003ECan replicate without mods?\u003C/strong\u003E Yes\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EOS:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0Windows 10 | \u003Cstrong\u003ECPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0i9 9900K | \u003Cstrong\u003EGPU:\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A03070ti | \u003Cstrong\u003ERAM\u003Cspan\u003E:\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E32GB\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:20px;\u0022\u003EObserved Behavior:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe Flight View camera angle is changing on returning from Map View, and is regularly ending up in the middle of the craft.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:20px;\u0022\u003EExpected Behavior:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nWhen going from Flight View to Map View and than back again, the Flight View camera angle and distance should be\u003Cstrong\u003E identical\u003C/strong\u003E to what it was before.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#c0392b;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:20px;\u0022\u003ESteps to Replicate:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nLoad \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprog